WEBVTT

00:02.997 --> 00:04.598
Would you pass
the mustard?

00:04.600 --> 00:05.699
Sure.

00:05.701 --> 00:07.534
Hey, want to hear
a fun fact about mustard?

00:07.536 --> 00:10.437
Is it that the glucosinolates
which give mustard its flavor

00:10.439 --> 00:11.805
were evolved
by the cabbage family

00:11.807 --> 00:14.441
as a chemical defense
against caterpillars?

00:14.443 --> 00:16.076
Yeah.

00:17.445 --> 00:19.246
Well, that was fun.

00:19.248 --> 00:21.381
Good for you, Leonard.

00:21.383 --> 00:22.916
Hey, there.

00:22.918 --> 00:23.917
Hey, you're early.

00:23.919 --> 00:25.652
The movie doesn't start
for an hour.

00:25.654 --> 00:27.287
Actually, we're not
going to the movies.

00:27.289 --> 00:29.956
We are here to kidnap you.

00:29.958 --> 00:31.291
What are you talking about?

00:31.293 --> 00:33.093
Well, you eloped and
we didn't get a chance

00:33.095 --> 00:34.527
to throw you
a bachelor party,

00:34.529 --> 00:36.062
so there's
a van downstairs

00:36.064 --> 00:37.697
and we're here
to take you

00:37.699 --> 00:39.699
to a surprise location
for the weekend.

00:39.701 --> 00:41.868
Well, I'd hardly
call this kidnapping.

00:41.870 --> 00:43.036
Where's the blindfold?

00:43.038 --> 00:44.271
Where's the duct tape?

00:44.273 --> 00:45.839
Where's the part

00:45.841 --> 00:47.574
where you call me
and demand ransom

00:47.576 --> 00:49.075
and I try to keep you
on the phone,

00:49.077 --> 00:51.344
but you hang up
seconds before I can trace it

00:51.346 --> 00:54.714
and then I say, "I'm getting
too old for this crud"?

00:56.884 --> 00:58.952
When do we leave?

00:58.954 --> 00:59.886
Right now.

00:59.888 --> 01:01.254
Yeah, Penny packed
you a bag.

01:01.256 --> 01:02.822
Wow, okay.

01:02.824 --> 01:04.724
You're seriously going to get
in a van and let these two

01:04.726 --> 01:05.992
take you
to an unknown destination

01:05.994 --> 01:07.460
for an entire weekend?

01:07.462 --> 01:09.362
Oh, not just him;
you're coming, too.

01:09.364 --> 01:11.998
Oh, and how do you think you're
going to get me to do that?

01:12.000 --> 01:13.033
Unhand me!

01:13.035 --> 01:14.067
This is ridiculous!

01:14.069 --> 01:15.602
I told you to put tape
on his mouth!

01:15.604 --> 01:17.804
And I told you he bit me!

